-You have to travel all over a mansion full of monsters to find the combination to a safe.<br>
-Taxi cabs can push buses out of their way.<br>
-You have a bar that tells you exactly how much life you have.<br>
-People don't have washrooms in their houses.<br>
-Shooting someone in the head and killing them will result in a loud voice saying, &quot;Head Shot.&quot;<br>
-You only get 100 health.<br>
-Cid likes to be in Final Fantasy.<br>
-There's a tank down by the docks just waiting to be stolen.<br>
-Cars can be crushed and turned into weapons.<br>
