<br>
2. No matter how many bullets are left in your gun, reloading only takes 3 seconds and you reload exactly the amount of bullets needed to replenish your magazine.<br>
<br>
3. You CAN jump 14 feet high; and by jumping twice, you can do multiple flips, too.<br>
<br>
4. Armor covers your entire body and no harm will come to you until every bit of the armor is destroyed.<br>
<br>
5. Never trust the bald guy.  He's a traitor.<br>
<br>
6. For the 40th time you moron, the princess is in ANOTHER castle.  How many times do we have to tell you this?<br>
<br>
7. Inevitably, you will be forced to kill your brother, sister, father, or son.  It's just the way it has to be.<br>
<br>
8. Get a sidekick.  He'll die shortly anyway but he'll amuse you in the meantime.<br>
<br>
9. &quot;Go, go, go!&quot;, &quot;Taking fire, need assistance!&quot;, or &quot;Get in position and wait for my go!&quot; are just jokes in the world of military ops.  No one will listen.<br>
<br>
10. Getting shot in the foot with a sniper rifle WILL kill you.  Deal.  No limp, no dragging of the leg, just death.<br>
<br>
11. When surrounded by the CIA, police, and national guard, simply take your battered taxi and drive it into a paint shop, re-paint it yellow, and drive away.  No one will ever catch on. <p>The surest sign of intelligent life in the universe is that none<BR>of it has tried contacting us.<BR>

